graph LR
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Web UI & API]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|resource mgmt<br/>HTTPS/443| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API 1.25+]
    Dashboard -->|routes & oauth<br/>HTTPS/443| OpenShift[OpenShift API 4.12+]
    Dashboard -->|authentication<br/>OAuth 2.0| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth]
    Dashboard -->|runtime| NodeJS[Node.js 18+]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|status queries<br/>API| ODHOperator[ODH Operator<br/>DataScienceCluster]
    Dashboard -->|create/manage<br/>Notebook CRD| Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks]
    Dashboard -->|manage runtimes<br/>ServingRuntime CRD| KServe[KServe]
    Dashboard -->|model deployment<br/>API| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving]
    Dashboard -->|pipeline mgmt<br/>HTTPS/8443| Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines]
    Dashboard -->|model versioning<br/>HTTPS/8080| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    Dashboard -->|metrics queries<br/>HTTPS/9092| Thanos[Thanos Querier<br/>Prometheus]

    %% External Services
    Dashboard -->|artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443| S3[S3 Storage<br/>Optional]

    %% Integration Points (Reverse Dependencies)
    ConsoleLink[OpenShift Console<br/>ConsoleLink] -.->|app menu| Dashboard
    Users[Data Scientists<br/>ML Engineers] -->|web access<br/>HTTPS/443| Dashboard

    %% Configuration Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|reads config| CRDs[Custom Resources<br/>OdhDashboardConfig<br/>OdhApplication<br/>AcceleratorProfile]

